 2. 請用餐= Que aproveche=Bon Appétit in french 
i hear people using "que aproveche" more than "Que disfrute" 

south american usually say  "aprovecho" or "buen aprovecho" 

 2009-08-11 01:25:55 補充： 
"provecho" or "buen provecho", no a, typo





